about my ancestors?

243
00:13:22,459 --> 00:13:23,042
Ning.

244
00:13:23,167 --> 00:13:24,417
What exactly is your
connection with your boss?

245
00:13:24,542 --> 00:13:25,584
Don't you find it weird?

246
